Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices NW Real Estate

data.description: Beautiful 3 bed/2 bath Golden West MFH on private cul-de-sac in 55+ gated community of the Beautiful Florentine Estates! Features Bright & Spacious extended living room, kitchen w/island, breakfast nook & lots of counter space, Dishwasher, Bi Micro, and corner window. Dining room with slider to private deck and beautifully landscaped side yard. Nice Master on opposite end for privacy. Double 24x27' garage attaches to a 15x27' hobby/craft room that enters into master bedroom with a removable ramp. Bathrooms have high rise toilets, Ceiling lights are reinforced for ceiling fans. Beautiful Large front deck. Greenbelt across the street. Decks were replaced approx 2019 and all re-stained. Engineering report on file for tie down installation. 2 car xlarge garage. All Poly piping replaced July 2022. Roof 2008.
